<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1593261-the-summary-states-that-little-dog">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[The summary states that Little Dog recounts his history, beginning before he was born and, "all of it leading to an unforgettable revelation". We learn he was abused, he's gay, he loved Trevor and his family, forgiving all their imperfections. Did I miss something? What was the unforgettable revelation? Ma's forced abortion? No revelation seems to stand out more than any other. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
