<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1742037-did-any-of-you-make-sense-of-the-reference">Did any of you make sense of the reference to Monarch butterflies at the beginning and end of this novel?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1742037'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F41880609-on-earth-we-re-briefly-gorgeous">like</a></span>

