<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/19736285-macgregor-obergfell"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1514395740i/19736285._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/19736285-macgregor-obergfell">MacGregor Obergfell</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I thought the butterflies symbolize his life journey. They do not know where they are going - the journey is imprinted in their subconscious. Much in <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I thought the butterflies symbolize his life journey. They do not know where they are going - the journey is imprinted in their subconscious. Much in the same way the butterflies have to trust their instincts and those who came before them and overcome hardships on a seemingly never-ending journey, so too is Little Dog doing the same in his life. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
