  <span id="freeText16207126304346315096" style="display:none">No review. Just a list of adjectives.<br /><br />Brutal<br />Raw<br />Devastating<br />Beautiful<br />Incandescent<br />Stunning<br /><br />The author didn't write this book; he opened his heart and just let it bleed all over the pages. Reading it cracked mine open and turned me inside out.<br /><br />Just a sample: "Did you know people get rich off of sadness? I want to meet the millionaire of American sadness. I want to look him in the eye, shake his hand, and say, "Its been an honor to serve my country".</span>
